      "category": "NEWS",
      "date": "Mar 26, 2026",
      "html": "<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5811afa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5811afa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">SXMA Awards 2026 nominations are now officially announced.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">This year’s shortlist brings together a wide range of companies, creators and projects shaping the future of the industry across categories including social media campaigns, design, community engagement, media, audio content and creative collaborations. The selection reflects both scale and originality, highlighting those who are actively defining current trends and industry leadership.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a949fd7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a949fd7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea279f0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ea279f0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7085af elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c7085af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"345\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/3333.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1436\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/3333.webp 345w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/3333-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/3333-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa97e85 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"aa97e85\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a146cb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0a146cb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"345\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/22222.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1435\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/22222.webp 345w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/22222-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/22222-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e38300f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e38300f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bcb98c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bcb98c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"345\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1-2.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1434\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1-2.webp 345w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1-2-300x300-2.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1-2-150x150-2.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e178d9a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e178d9a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ae6eea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3ae6eea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">The nominations present a cross section of established brands, emerging voices and independent creators whose work has had a visible impact over the past year. From product innovation and digital presence to storytelling and community building, the list captures the diversity and evolution of the sector.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Public voting will open on 1 April 2026, allowing the wider community to take part in selecting the finalists. The SXMA Awards continue to position themselves as a platform recognising both commercial success and creative contribution within the global landscape.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">VOTE 1.04.2025 </span><a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://sxma.sxtech.eu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HERE</a></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5466ac5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5466ac5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68505d1 elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"68505d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">join our<br />newsletter</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fa04a8 elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"5fa04a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">BECOME A SPONSOR</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>"
